title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Treasonous Fits
description:
Jimmy and Larry: truly our last hope to save democracy as we know it. This week, the boys are linking up to hold the line against potential coups, insurrection highlights, Bottega Venetta deleting social media, Kim and Kanye’s divorce, Harry Styles cucking Jason Sudeikis, The Weeknd’s latest transformation, the CIA’s rebrand and much more. Plus, remembering your favorite MC’s favorite MC, MF Doom. Rest in power.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
